data.description: Beautiful home in Sun Ridge, located near Loop 375, shopping and restaurants. Home has vaulted ceilings and plentiful natural light, 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms. Equipped with refrigerated air, plantation shutters and an attached 2 vehicle garage. RV parking with large metal side gate. Fully landscaped front and rear with above ground pool.Extended privacy rockwalls in back yard. 5.625% Assumable Interest rate call for details.
